headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Johnson Controls (JCI) After Its 73% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Johnson Controls International is still good value after its recent run, this article will walk through what the current share price could mean for long term investors. The stock last closed at US$142.83, with returns of 2.6% over 7 days, 25.7% over 30 days, 16.8% year to date and 72.6% over 1 year. The 3 year and 5 year returns stand at 142.0% and 176.8% respectively. Recent price moves have arrived alongside ongoing interest in building efficiency, automation...
